# Production frontend env vars — embedded into the Vite build at build time.
# These are PUBLIC values by design (OAuth client ID, Paystack public key, public API URLs).
# They appear in the shipped JS bundle anyway; storing them here lets CI builds work.
# For sensitive values (Paystack SECRET key, JWT_SECRET, etc.), use Cloudflare Worker secrets.

